BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 744.00 Tm (### 4.4 Workflow Process Text Flow) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 718.00 Tm (The route `POST /api/v1/workflows/process-text`:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 692.00 Tm (1. stores the text as a source,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 679.00 Tm (2. extracts structured data,) Tj ET
