BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 627.00 Tm (### 4.5 Slack Channel Slash Command Flow) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 601.00 Tm (The route `POST /slack/commands` forwards to Slack Bolt.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 575.00 Tm (The command handler supports channel usage like:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 549.00 Tm (- `/followthru`) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 536.00 Tm (- `/followthru publish`) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 523.00 Tm (- `/followthru help`) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 510.00 Tm (- `/followthru process <zoom-link>`) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 484.00 Tm (For channel preview/publish:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 458.00 Tm (1. FollowThru resolves the latest huddle notes canvas or transcript.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 445.00 Tm (2. It extracts structured meeting intelligence.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 432.00 Tm (3. It returns an ephemeral preview or publishes to the channel canvas.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 406.00 Tm (### 4.6 Slack DM Flow) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 380.00 Tm (In DMs, the bot can:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 354.00 Tm (- reply with help,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 341.00 Tm (- clear chat state,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 328.00 Tm (- stop active ingestion jobs,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 315.00 Tm (- accept pasted transcript text,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 302.00 Tm (- accept uploaded transcript files,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 60.00 289.00 Tm (- generate draft/preview/publish outputs.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 263.00 Tm (The DM handler is more flexible than the channel handler because it supports direct raw) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 250.00 Tm (content.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 224.00 Tm (### 4.7 Async Video Processing Flow) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 198.00 Tm (The new recording flow works like this:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 172.00 Tm (1. User runs `/followthru process <Zoom-recording-link>`.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 159.00 Tm (2. FollowThru opens a modal with extraction choices.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 146.00 Tm (3. User submits the modal.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 133.00 Tm (4. Slack interaction handler immediately acknowledges the modal.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 120.00 Tm (5. The handler posts a status message and enqueues `process_meeting_task`.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 107.00 Tm (6. Celery downloads the recording.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 94.00 Tm (7. FFmpeg extracts and chunks audio.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10.00 Tf 1 0 0 1 48.00 81.00 Tm (8. Whisper transcribes the audio chunks in parallel.) Tj ET
endstream
